USB, VGA, multi-functional output

2.5.3 Battery Back Board

The iMEC patient monitor consumes low power thanks to the better system design. One lithium battery is capable to

supply the power for the whole system. The battery back board transmits the signal of battery capacity and status into

the internal system. The patient monitor only supports lithium battery. The on-site detection of lithium battery is

achieved by the resistance inside the battery. A new battery provides two types of information by 2 pins:

 Battery on-site information

 Battery low/high capacity information



# Página 13

**Equipo:** Monitor multiparametrico IMEC

